<section xml:id="ftp.installation" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
 &reftitle.install;
 <para>
  In order to use FTP functions with your PHP configuration, you should
  add the <option role="configure">--enable-ftp</option> option when
  installing PHP.
 </para>
 <para>
  On Windows this extension is always built as shared extension
  and as such has to be enabled in &php.ini;.
 </para>
</section>

